{"tid":224579,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"搞唔懂的科幻電影 : The Signal","createTime":"2017-05-01T07:20:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T11:50:26.000Z","uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eae5705926218fd1bb0ff2a9148eeb66a5c79d45","tid":224579,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T07:20:02.000Z","msg":"睇緊個陣以為劇情只向一方發展<br />\n點知越黎越後反而留底更多迷團，睇完搞到一頭霧水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老實好鐘意呢類型既科幻片，特別拍攝鏡頭同氣氛<br />\n不時串插主角同其他兩位既回憶有種浪漫係到，轉眼間一幕就換成科幻片<br />\n<br />\n不過劇情真係留白左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，網上又搵唔到導演解釋，睇完好似無睇咁<br />\n所以套戲有垃圾爛片既聲音都唔奇，如果套戲肯去完整少少個劇情成為經典都有可能<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/b78df5f15a4040e7af68af9a8e8699ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fb78df5f15a4040e7af68af9a8e8699ee.jpg&h=acfa388a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6cc14352692e50b43ee646d7255dccd389cca1a1","tid":224579,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T16:47:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4637868b578668594a3f73682312306e32787074","tid":224579,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T11:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}